Question: Describe what you did last weekend.
Answer:
i went to asian supermarket for shopping last week. it was about 4 hours driving. there were about five persons on the car. my car is a compact two door vehicle. therefore, the room is a little small for five adults. it was a nice trip. we chatted and shared lots of interesting stories. it really was very funny. the supermarket is very big and the supplies are very rich. we bought so many things that the trunk was totally full. after that we went to a very famous restaurant and enjoyed their delicious food. since we had already booked the table before, we did not need to wait there. it took us about two hours there, and everyone of us is very satisfied with their service. 